    "description": [
        "Episode number 4 of Series \"Arkady Leokum's Tell Me Why\". This program presents and answers questions about gems, metals and minerals. Let your children see where soil and sand comes from. Answer puzzling questions like: Why are there so many different kinds of rocks? What is atomic weight? Where do pearls come from? Quick search numbers appear on screen to help you find the section you want to view. Based on the series of books by Arkady Leokum."
